    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2) features the refined 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six, delivering 320hp through a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. The powerplant benefits from a verified IMS bearing retrofit and a recently replaced rear main seal, addressing critical M96 architecture concerns. Handling is sharpened by an OE-spec Bilstein damper setup and fresh bushings across the multi-link rear suspension. The VarioCam Plus system ensures a linear torque curve, while the four-piston Monobloc Brembo calipers provide fade-resistant deceleration. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history, this 911 offers an authentic analog driving experience with a chassis that remains taut and responsive under load.",
      "price": 34500.0,
