      "description": "This meticulously cared-for sedan strikes the perfect balance between luxury and reliability. The exterior retains a deep, glossy shine, showing only the minor road-wear one would expect from a well-loved vehicle. Inside, the premium leather upholstery has been preserved beautifully, and every electronic feature\u2014from the responsive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014functions exactly as it should. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and smoothly, benefiting from a documented history of on-time oil changes and preventative maintenance. We recently fitted a fresh set of all-season tires and performed a full brake service, ensuring this car is road-trip ready the moment you turn the key. It\u2019s a solid, dependable choice for anyone seeking a premium driving experience without the new-car price tag. Clean title in hand and ready for a smooth transition to its next owner.",
